[Jamal Speaks Hindi ]

1:00:23.870 --> 1:00:26.038
[ Latika ]
I know ifyou're looking.

1:00:26.122 --> 1:00:28.332
No, I'm not.

1:00:28.416 --> 1:00:30.417
[ Latika ]
Is Salim still there?

1:00:34.213 --> 1:00:36.214
[ Shower Water Running ]

1:00:37.258 --> 1:00:39.259
Where's Salim?

1:00:39.344 --> 1:00:41.345
[ Car Horns Honking ]

1:00:42.972 --> 1:00:44.973
Don't know.

1:00:47.685 --> 1:00:49.686
You're a sweet boy,Jamal.

1:01:02.575 --> 1:01:05.452
- ♪♪ [ Hip-hop ]
- [ Horns Honking ]

1:01:05.536 --> 1:01:09.122
♪♪ [ Singing
In Foreign Language ]

1:01:25.139 --> 1:01:27.933
[ Shouting ]

1:01:35.858 --> 1:01:39.403
[ Cheering, Laughing ]

1:01:41.364 --> 1:01:44.449
I'm looking forJaved.

1:01:44.534 --> 1:01:46.993
[ Hindi ]
He's not looking
foryou.

1:01:51.332 --> 1:01:53.750
I killed Maman.

1:01:53.835 --> 1:01:55.794
And I'll kill you too.

1:01:59.882 --> 1:02:01.758
Easy.

1:02:01.843 --> 1:02:04.678
[Javed ]
Did you really kill him?

1:02:10.226 --> 1:02:11.393
Good.

1:02:11.477 --> 1:02:14.563
My enemy's enemy
is a friend.

1:02:17.358 --> 1:02:19.401
Come here, my friend.

1:02:23.740 --> 1:02:27.784
Mm. I've been looking
for someone like you.

1:02:34.834 --> 1:02:37.335
You came back for me.

1:02:39.046 --> 1:02:41.089
Ofcourse.

1:02:43.926 --> 1:02:46.720
I thought you'd forgotten.

1:02:48.181 --> 1:02:52.100
I never forgot.
Not for one moment.

1:02:52.185 --> 1:02:54.895
I knew I'd find you
in the end.

1:02:54.979 --> 1:02:58.023
It's our destiny.

1:02:59.317 --> 1:03:01.318
Destiny.

1:03:02.779 --> 1:03:04.780
[ Hindi ]

1:03:20.713 --> 1:03:23.381
Hey.

1:03:23.466 --> 1:03:26.843
[ Groans ]

1:03:26.928 --> 1:03:30.472
Come.

1:03:30.556 --> 1:03:33.099
No, Brother.
You've had a lot to drink.

1:03:33.184 --> 1:03:36.102
I am the elder.
I am the boss.

1:03:36.187 --> 1:03:38.980
For once you do
as I say.

1:03:39.065 --> 1:03:40.982
Now get out.

1:03:41.067 --> 1:03:43.777
Come on.
I saved your life, didn't I?

1:03:43.903 --> 1:03:45.821
Salim, please—
[ Hindi ]

1:03:45.905 --> 1:03:48.698
[ Screams ]
I'll kill you!

1:03:48.825 --> 1:03:50.492
Kill you!
[ Shouts ]

1:03:50.576 --> 1:03:52.869
[ Both Grunting ]

1:03:52.954 --> 1:03:56.164
[ Screaming ]

1:03:56.249 --> 1:03:57.749
I'll kill you!

1:04:02.255 --> 1:04:04.923
- [ Grunts ]
- I am number one now.

1:04:05.842 --> 1:04:07.551
[ Lock Clicks ]

1:04:07.635 --> 1:04:10.929
[ Grunts ]
Salim!

1:04:11.013 --> 1:04:14.015
Salim, open it!
[ Grunts, Shouts ]

1:04:14.100 --> 1:04:16.059
Shut up!

1:04:16.143 --> 1:04:18.144
The man with the Colt .45
says shut up!

1:04:18.229 --> 1:04:23.608
Go now, or Gunmaster G-9 will shoot you
right between the eyes.

1:04:24.610 --> 1:04:26.570
Don't think he won't.

1:04:26.654 --> 1:04:30.949
I'm giving you five seconds.
One,

1:04:32.743 --> 1:04:34.661
two—

1:04:37.498 --> 1:04:38.665
Go,Jamal.

1:04:39.876 --> 1:04:41.793
Go.

1:04:44.589 --> 1:04:46.506
[ Hindi ]

1:04:52.471 --> 1:04:54.472
[ Lock Clicks ]

1:05:06.611 --> 1:05:10.405
So, did you
see them again?

1:05:10.489 --> 1:05:12.699
I wouldn't be here
if I had.

1:05:14.660 --> 1:05:16.661
Was she pretty?

1:05:18.497 --> 1:05:21.333
I guess not.

1:05:23.252 --> 1:05:25.670
The most beautiful
woman in the world.

1:05:25.755 --> 1:05:27.964
He means "the bitch
ofthe slums."
[ Laughs ]

1:05:28.049 --> 1:05:30.717
- [ Both Shouting ]
- Hey. Hey!

1:05:30.801 --> 1:05:35.639
- Hey, no--
- [ Shouting Continues ]

1:05:36.891 --> 1:05:39.935
[ Speaking Hindi ]

1:05:40.019 --> 1:05:42.270
[ Hindi ]
Well, well.

1:05:42.355 --> 1:05:44.105
The slumdog barks.

1:05:44.231 --> 1:05:46.691
[ Scoffs ]
Money and women—

1:05:46.776 --> 1:05:48.944
the reasons to make
most mistakes in life.

1:05:49.028 --> 1:05:50.695
[ Srinivas ]
Correct.

1:05:50.780 --> 1:05:52.739
Looks like you're
mixed up with both.

1:05:55.618 --> 1:05:57.535
Srinivas.
[ Hindi ]

1:05:57.620 --> 1:05:59.913
You need the exercise.

1:05:59.997 --> 1:06:02.958
Go and get me something
to eat.

1:06:03.042 --> 1:06:04.960
Yes, sir.

1:06:05.044 --> 1:06:07.003
And chai.

1:06:09.131 --> 1:06:11.049
Phaode!

1:06:18.057 --> 1:06:20.225
Idiot, Srinivas.

1:06:26.482 --> 1:06:28.400
You puzzle me, slumdog—

1:06:28.484 --> 1:06:32.445
admitting murder to avoid
the charge offraud...

1:06:32.530 --> 1:06:34.864
is not exactly
clever thinking.

1:06:37.159 --> 1:06:39.869
Now, why would you do that?

1:06:39.954 --> 1:06:42.080
Hmm?

1:06:42.164 --> 1:06:45.250
When somebody asks me
a question,

1:06:45.334 --> 1:06:47.460
I tell them the answer.

1:06:49.505 --> 1:06:51.506
Hmm.

1:06:53.759 --> 1:06:57.929
So, how did you manage
to get on the show?
[ Glasses Rattling ]

1:06:58.014 --> 1:07:00.181
[ Chattering ]

1:07:00.266 --> 1:07:02.183
[ Woman ]
Okay, everyone.
Listen up.

1:07:02.268 --> 1:07:05.562
It's been a big week
for U.K.

1:07:05.646 --> 1:07:07.564
Kat is back.

1:07:07.690 --> 1:07:09.482
[ Groaning ]
But she was already back.

1:07:09.567 --> 1:07:11.901
Bardi.Jamal?

1:07:13.195 --> 1:07:15.989
Oh, well, she did come back.
Then she went away...

1:07:16.073 --> 1:07:19.117
when Alfie split up with her,
and now she's back again.

1:07:19.201 --> 1:07:21.411
But it looks as if
Alfie still fancies Mo after all.

1:07:21.495 --> 1:07:23.913
Thankyou,Jamal.
Bardi, keep up.

1:07:24.040 --> 1:07:27.083
The chai wallah knows
more than you.
[ Laughter ]

1:07:27.168 --> 1:07:30.879
Anyway, there's also
the festival in Edinburgh.

1:07:30.963 --> 1:07:33.673
Anybody knows Edinburgh?
Edinburgh?

1:07:33.758 --> 1:07:38.428
Ah, kilts, castles,
uh, haggis, uh, Ben Nevis.

1:07:38.512 --> 1:07:40.430
[ Teacher ]
Good. Yes?

1:07:40.514 --> 1:07:44.059
[ Young Man ]
InspectorTaggart,
whiskey, Sean Connery.

1:07:44.143 --> 1:07:47.479
[ Teacher ]
Good. And lochs--
theirword for lakes.

1:07:47.563 --> 1:07:49.481
No filming.

1:07:55.154 --> 1:07:58.156
Jamal, come here.

1:07:58.240 --> 1:08:00.450
I'm on Millionaire duty
today.

1:08:00.534 --> 1:08:03.328
- Dave—
- Please.
Just for five minutes.

1:08:03.412 --> 1:08:04.746
I can't.

1:08:04.830 --> 1:08:07.373
Sit here.
Ifthe team leader comes,

1:08:07.500 --> 1:08:10.835
just pretend you are on a call
doing an upgrade for--
Friends and Family. I know.

1:08:10.961 --> 1:08:12.921
Yah.
Two minutes.

1:08:13.005 --> 1:08:14.506
Ah.

1:08:18.427 --> 1:08:20.720
Who Wants to Be
a Millionaire?

1:08:20.805 --> 1:08:23.556
Dial this number now.

1:08:23.641 --> 1:08:27.602
Answer this question.
What does "A.T.M."—
[ Continues, Indistinct ]

1:08:27.686 --> 1:08:29.771
Hello? Hello? Hello?

1:08:29.855 --> 1:08:33.149
I would like to be a contestant
on Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?

1:08:33.275 --> 1:08:35.568
[ Man ]
Hello? I want to be on—
Uh—

1:08:35.653 --> 1:08:38.488
Bloody bastard.
I never get it!

1:08:38.572 --> 1:08:40.990
You have to dial
when Prem says "if."

1:08:41.117 --> 1:08:44.202
That's when they
open the lines.
How the hell do you know that?

1:08:44.286 --> 1:08:47.497
That's what Anjum
in technical says.
He put the system in.

1:08:47.581 --> 1:08:50.250
[ Woman On Phone,
Scottish Accent ]
Hello? Hello?

1:08:50.334 --> 1:08:53.336
Have I been transferred again,
for God's sake?

1:08:53.420 --> 1:08:57.674
Hello? Good God,
will somebody talk to me?

1:08:57.758 --> 1:08:59.801
Uh, hello,

1:08:59.885 --> 1:09:04.305
Mrs. Mackintosh
from... "King-uss-ie."

1:09:04.390 --> 1:09:08.560
It's Kingussie, love.
Pronounced "Kingussie."

1:09:08.644 --> 1:09:11.396
So where are you from?
Abroad, I bet.

1:09:11.480 --> 1:09:14.732
[ Scottish Accent ]
Uh,just down the road from
your house, Mrs. Mackintosh.

1:09:14.817 --> 1:09:16.442
Uh, next to the loch.

1:09:16.527 --> 1:09:19.279
Och aye?
Which loch?

1:09:19.363 --> 1:09:21.406
Loch—

1:09:21.490 --> 1:09:25.034
Loch—
Big... Loch Ben.

1:09:25.119 --> 1:09:28.872
Loch Big Ben. Next door
to Sean Connery's flat.

1:09:28.956 --> 1:09:31.708
- I'd like to speak to
your supervisor, son.
- [ Taps Keyboard ]

1:09:31.792 --> 1:09:34.711
[ Dial Tone ]

1:09:34.795 --> 1:09:37.255
[ Sighs ]

1:09:41.177 --> 1:09:59.444
[ Typing ]

1:10:03.657 --> 1:10:04.782
[ Taps Key ]

1:10:14.210 --> 1:10:17.837
- [ Dialing ]
- [ Line Ringing ]

1:10:19.089 --> 1:10:21.758
- [ Man ]
Yes?
- Salim?

1:10:21.884 --> 1:10:25.094
Who is this?
Do you know what time is this?
[ Taps Key ]

1:10:28.265 --> 1:10:30.266
[ Typing ]
[ Dialing ]

1:10:30.351 --> 1:10:34.687
[ Line Ringing ]
[ Man ]
Hello?

1:10:34.813 --> 1:10:36.648
[ Taps Key ]
[ Monitor Chimes ]

1:10:41.654 --> 1:10:43.947
- [ Taps Keys ]
- [ Dialing ]

1:10:44.031 --> 1:10:47.492
[ Line Ringing ]

1:10:47.576 --> 1:10:51.412
[ Salim ]
Hello? Hello?

1:10:51.497 --> 1:10:53.957
[ Chimes ]
Who is this?

1:10:56.085 --> 1:10:58.836
I'm calling from
XL 5 Communications, sir.

1:10:58.921 --> 1:11:01.381
As a valued customer, we are
offering you a free upgrade...

1:11:01.465 --> 1:11:03.299
with our Friends and—

1:11:03.384 --> 1:11:05.426
♪♪ [ Suspenseful Theme ]

1:11:05.511 --> 1:11:07.470
Family--

1:11:07.554 --> 1:11:10.014
Jamal?

1:11:10.099 --> 1:11:12.809
I-Is that you, Brother?

1:11:12.893 --> 1:11:15.853
Where are you? I thought you
were dead or something.

1:11:15.938 --> 1:11:18.690
Listen.
We had to go,Jamal.

1:11:18.774 --> 1:11:22.777
Maman's guys— they were
searching the hotel.

1:11:22.861 --> 1:11:26.489
Jamal? Say something,
please!

1:11:27.783 --> 1:11:30.535
Hello, Salim.

1:11:30.619 --> 1:11:32.787
[ Prem ]
Cambridge Circus
is not in Cambridge.

1:11:32.871 --> 1:11:34.914
Dare I ask why?

1:11:34.999 --> 1:11:36.749
Too obvious.

1:11:36.834 --> 1:11:38.918
There's definitely
an Oxford Circus in London.

1:11:39.003 --> 1:11:43.965
And there's a rowing race
between Oxford and Cambridge,
so there's probably...

1:11:44.049 --> 1:11:46.009
a Cambridge Circus too, no?

1:11:46.093 --> 1:11:48.261
I'll go for "D," London.

1:11:48.345 --> 1:11:53.808
Computer-ji,
"D" lock kiya-jaye.

1:12:00.232 --> 1:12:02.859
Jamal Malik,

1:12:02.985 --> 1:12:05.236
you're absolutely right!
[ Cheering ]

1:12:10.617 --> 1:12:12.869
[ Cheering Continues ]

1:12:15.164 --> 1:12:17.540
- [ Prem ]
It's getting hot in here.
- [ Laughter ]

1:12:17.666 --> 1:12:19.709
Are you nervous?
What?

1:12:19.835 --> 1:12:22.587
[ Laughter ]
Am I nervous?

1:12:22.671 --> 1:12:25.256
It's you who's in
the hot seat, my friend.

1:12:25.341 --> 1:12:27.216
Oh, yes.

1:12:27.343 --> 1:12:29.469
Sorry.
[ Laughter ]

1:12:29.553 --> 1:12:31.846
[ Laughs ]
Bloody hell,
he's got Prem on the run.

1:12:31.972 --> 1:12:34.557
Finally.
A few hours ago,

1:12:34.641 --> 1:12:38.728
you were giving chai
for the phone wallahs.

1:12:38.812 --> 1:12:42.440
And now you're richer
than they will ever be.

1:12:42.524 --> 1:12:44.984
What a player.

1:12:45.069 --> 1:12:47.195
Ladies and gentlemen,
what a player!

1:12:47.279 --> 1:12:49.614
[ Cheering ]

1:12:49.698 --> 1:12:54.202
[ Cheering Fades ]
[ Mechanical Whirring ]

1:13:29.780 --> 1:13:31.823
Jamal?

1:13:33.867 --> 1:13:37.036
God is good, bhai.
God is good.

1:13:37.162 --> 1:13:38.830
[ Grunts ]
[ Screams ]

1:13:38.914 --> 1:13:41.874
[ Both Scream ]

1:13:46.463 --> 1:13:48.339
[ Grunts ]

1:13:53.095 --> 1:13:56.139
Maman's guys were after us.
Wejust had to skip.

1:13:56.265 --> 1:13:58.558
Liar.
Left a message
foryou at work.

1:13:58.684 --> 1:14:01.436
Waited weeks foryou
at Nagpur.
There was no message.

1:14:01.520 --> 1:14:03.563
Bhai, I definitely
left a message.

1:14:03.647 --> 1:14:07.733
There was no message.
There was no message!
There was no message!

1:14:12.322 --> 1:14:14.866
I will never forgive you.

1:14:19.788 --> 1:14:22.707
I know.

1:14:26.462 --> 1:14:29.380
That used to be
our slum.

1:14:31.091 --> 1:14:33.050
Can you believe that, huh?

1:14:33.135 --> 1:14:36.053
We used to live
right there, man.

1:14:38.223 --> 1:14:41.184
Now it's all business.

1:14:41.268 --> 1:14:45.062
India is at the center
ofthe world hub, bhai.

1:14:45.147 --> 1:14:47.064
And I—

1:14:47.149 --> 1:14:49.108
I am at the center...

1:14:49.193 --> 1:14:51.444
ofthe center.

1:14:53.322 --> 1:14:55.907
This is all Javed-bhai's.

1:14:57.659 --> 1:15:00.953
-Javed Khan?
- Sorry.

1:15:01.038 --> 1:15:03.247
[Jamal ]
The gangster from our slum?
You work for him?

1:15:03.332 --> 1:15:07.084
Come on. Who else do you think would
save us from Maman's guys, huh?

1:15:07.169 --> 1:15:09.128
What do you do for him?

1:15:11.256 --> 1:15:13.216
Anything he asks.

1:15:16.762 --> 1:15:20.890
♪♪ [ Ring Tone ]
[ Beeps ]

1:15:20.974 --> 1:15:24.143
He's coming.
You need to go now.

1:15:24.269 --> 1:15:27.104
Take my card.
What for?

1:15:27.189 --> 1:15:30.316
You think I'm gonna let you
out of my sights again, huh?

1:15:30.400 --> 1:15:32.443
You stay with me now,
younger brother.

1:15:32.528 --> 1:15:34.946
Now go— my place.

1:15:35.030 --> 1:15:38.115
Salim, where is Latika?

1:15:38.200 --> 1:15:40.243
Still?

1:15:43.705 --> 1:15:48.417
She's gone, Brother.
Long gone. Now go.

1:15:48.502 --> 1:15:51.045
Go to my place.

1:15:59.137 --> 1:16:02.515
[ Vehicles Passing ]
[ Horns Honking ]

1:16:07.938 --> 1:16:10.106
♪♪ [ Cell Phone: Ring Tone ]

1:16:10.190 --> 1:16:12.984
♪♪ [ Man Scatting ]
[ Phone Beeps ]

1:16:13.068 --> 1:16:14.986
♪ Hey ♪
Hello?

1:16:15.070 --> 1:16:16.862
Okay, I'll be right there.

1:16:16.947 --> 1:16:19.323
♪♪ [ Scatting Continues ]

1:16:43.223 --> 1:16:46.684
♪♪ [ Singing
In Foreign Language ]

1:16:50.772 --> 1:16:53.149
[ Hindi ]

1:17:02.784 --> 1:17:12.084
♪ Hey ♪

1:17:22.262 --> 1:17:24.221
[ Indistinct ]

1:17:26.016 --> 1:17:27.933
♪♪ [ Continues ]

1:17:32.773 --> 1:17:34.732
♪ Hey ♪

1:17:35.776 --> 1:17:37.485
♪ Hey ♪♪
[ Hindi ]

1:17:37.569 --> 1:17:40.363
I'm the new cook from the agency.
A thousand apologies.

1:17:40.447 --> 1:17:42.990
I am so late for the memsahib.

1:17:43.075 --> 1:17:44.992
Just a minute.

1:17:58.298 --> 1:18:00.508
[ Speaker: Feedback ]
[ Man ]
Excuse me.

1:18:00.592 --> 1:18:02.968
Excuse me.

1:18:03.053 --> 1:18:05.596
There's nothing about
any cook.

1:18:05.681 --> 1:18:07.848
There is a dishwasher
being delivered.

1:18:07.933 --> 1:18:10.184
Do you know anything
about that?

1:18:10.268 --> 1:18:13.813
[ Hindi ]
I am your dishwasher.

1:18:28.745 --> 1:18:31.622
♪♪ [ Woman Humming ]

1:19:07.576 --> 1:19:10.745
[ Gasps ]

1:19:15.083 --> 1:19:16.792
Jamal.

1:19:22.257 --> 1:19:24.425
Look at you.

1:19:30.807 --> 1:19:37.229
I found you.

1:19:44.905 --> 1:19:46.989
Your face.

1:19:47.073 --> 1:19:49.200
You've hurt your eye.

1:19:49.284 --> 1:19:51.535
Why are you here?

1:19:53.163 --> 1:19:55.080
To see you.

1:19:55.165 --> 1:19:58.793
Well, you see me.

1:19:58.877 --> 1:20:00.836
Now what?

1:20:00.921 --> 1:20:04.840
[ Prem On TV ]
"C," Eden's Bridge,

1:20:04.925 --> 1:20:07.343
or "D," Apple's Bridge.

1:20:09.471 --> 1:20:12.890
[ Chuckles ]
Why does everyone
love this program?

1:20:14.184 --> 1:20:18.854
It's a chance to escape,
isn't it?

1:20:18.939 --> 1:20:21.315
Walk into another life.

1:20:21.399 --> 1:20:24.235
- [ Horn Honks ]
- Oh, God.

1:20:27.906 --> 1:20:30.574
Javed will kill you.
Just— Here.

1:20:30.659 --> 1:20:33.577
Javed? You're with him?

1:20:43.839 --> 1:20:46.006
First you order
a dishwasher.

1:20:47.467 --> 1:20:49.385
Nowyou want this
fucking cook, huh?

1:20:49.469 --> 1:20:51.303
- I just thought—
- Shut up!

1:20:51.388 --> 1:20:55.391
- The cricket is on.
- [ Cheering On TV ]

1:20:55.475 --> 1:20:58.102
And why do you watch this
shit TV?

1:20:58.186 --> 1:21:00.855
As it is I am a millionaire.
[ Laughs ]

1:21:00.939 --> 1:21:02.982
[ Remote Control Clicks ]

1:21:03.066 --> 1:21:06.110
Come on. I'm hungry.
Make me a sandwich.

1:21:12.117 --> 1:21:14.201
[ Cheering On TV ]

1:21:20.876 --> 1:21:22.793
[Javed Speaking, Indistinct ]

1:21:22.878 --> 1:21:25.421
I want to bet five lakh rupees
he'll make a century.

1:21:25.505 --> 1:21:29.133
[ Continues, Indistinct ]

1:21:30.176 --> 1:21:32.803
Ah! Make it seven then.

